  <brief_title>Long-Standing Persistant Atrial Fibrillation-Pulmonary Vein Isolation With or Without Ablation</brief_title>
  <acronym>Alster-Lost</acronym>
  <official_title>Ablation at St. Georg Hospital for Long-Standing Persistent Atrial Fibrillation - Pulmonary Vein Isolation With or Without Ablation of Complex Fragmented Atrial Potentials</official_title>
